<!-- pages/index/index.wxml -->
<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="heart-icon">💗</view>
    <view class="header-title">恋爱依恋类型测试</view>
    <view class="header-subtitle">探索亲密关系中的自己</view>
  </view>
  
  <view class="main-content">
    <view class="welcome-card">
      <view class="welcome-title">了解你的依恋类型</view>
      <view class="welcome-desc">依恋类型决定了我们在亲密关系中的行为模式，了解它能帮助你更好地经营感情</view>
      
      <view class="features">
        <view class="feature-item">
          <view class="feature-icon">📝</view>
          <view class="feature-text">30道题目</view>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-item">
          <view class="feature-icon">⏱️</view>
          <view class="feature-text">约5分钟</view>
        </view>
        <view class="feature-item">
          <view class="feature-icon">💡</view>
          <view class="feature-text">自我探索</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      
      <button class="start-btn" bindtap="startTest">开始测试</button>
    </view>
  </view>
  
  <view class="disclaimer">
    <text>本测试仅供娱乐参考，不作为心理诊断依据。\n如有困扰，建议寻求专业心理咨询师帮助。</text>
  </view>
</view>